auth {
  mode: none
}

docs {
  This API manages **users**, each with a `username`, `password`, and `score`.  
  It supports basic CRUD operations and includes integration tests for all endpoints.
  
  ### Routes
  
  - `GET /users`  
    Retrieve all users.
  
  - `POST /users`  
    Add a new user. Requires `username`, `password`, and `score` in the body.
  
  - `DELETE /users/:username`  
    Delete a user by username.
  
  All routes handle errors and return clear status codes and messages.
}
